      • isSelectable

        public boolean isSelectable()
        This says whether this object is selectable on a page with a set The default as can be seen is true. Any dto class that cares should override this method. This is used by RhnSet in the select all method. In order to disable checkboxes on a page use <rhn:set value="${current.id}" disabled="${not current.selectable}" />
        Specified by:
